QueryOutcome

The outcome of processing a query request

This value set defines its own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/query-outcome

CodeDisplayDefinition
okThe query was processed successfully.
limitedThe query was processed successfully, but some additional limitations were added.
refusedThe server refused to process the query.
errorThe server tried to process the query, but some error occurred.
